Like that? If that&#39;s what you meant, then don&#39;t do that. You can just read in the data from the template file and output all the data at once. You could read it into a multiline text string of you could read the data in from the template and output it directly to the new file. Something like

    while( (strInput = templateFileReader.readLine()) != null)
